{
  "stem": "26880.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I wrote a letter to my wife, I had over there a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I had over there a lot, a lot of gold, silver, dollars, and should take out everything, what she could carry, from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And took-- and [NON-ENGLISH] was waiting for her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, no, she was killed, from the letter, what I wrote to her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't do nothing-- she was baking bread at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She took two bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She making bread-- I say, what you say, making bread?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could-- now, I can-- [MUMBLING].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, everything is left over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my luck it was, I had [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] $400 I had hiding in one place, and $400 from second place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The one place, it was-- like Europe, it was the stuffs, it was from brick.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I-- behind the stuff, I took up the bricks, and I put in over there, in a box, what my grandfather used to keep in tobacco, to smoke.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They put in-- I use-- I put in the dollars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was too hot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I came from the ghetto, I-- then I went over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was living over there by a chair-- shoemaker, actually.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No, I didn't ask him to do nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I took a hammer, and he came to my house, and took out-- and I took out that-- it was on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't tell him nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I came home, [INAUDIBLE] it was-- for the all dollars, it was pieces-- like small pieces-- and nothing was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No, I was-- no, I didn't want-- I threw it away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I took the same paper, and I was slipping [INAUDIBLE] where I went.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Until I came to America.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
